{"tid":421201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[少林功夫醒] 傳統足球 Calcio Storico","createTime":"2017-10-02T05:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T13:37:10.000Z","uid":89046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8091ad5213314dd95a55b272087f9c6f0770f7","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:03:12.000Z","msg":"佛羅倫斯傳統足球 16世紀流傳至今<br />\n27對27 每隊有4個龍 3個後衞 5個中場 15個前鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標係將個波送去對方場區個龍度<br />\n但係射龍如果高出嘅話 對方可以攞到半分 所以一係要射得好準 一係就先打柒曬對方班球員再輕鬆入龍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一場打足50分鐘冇暫停<br />\n唔可以換人 傷出冇替補<br />\n所以多數都係打到對面啲球員又傷又攰先會開始進攻 但規定只可以隻揪<br />\n<br />\n成場波亂到九彩 有啲人淨係識行行企企喺度freeride 屌佢老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2016 final<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UQzj6pcHAac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUQzj6pcHAac&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=50d635fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UQzj6pcHAac</a>"},{"pid":"cf611efc9afefab3e6d28d731803c00e7ba1ade8","tid":421201,"uid":39064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"4ddce7f4b542a4e484ff1d9926ca5fb8861bb53c","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"搵到段記錄片好正<br />\n8:20 開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WjDmNGXtKQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWjDmNGXtKQg&d=eWIWh0ev6rHAwRz%2FCIq26QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f9ccc5db\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WjDmNGXtKQg</a>"},{"pid":"75f2bfd0c0f1f24a322c74fc0a3efc86d827d03e","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b0296742cb8da28abe4976e914472aa0ef7c50","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3d62a68fef6b46f0f7783bf91d08e4f9066bfa","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e1c9676b1351ebf47c48f5b8d27612659d9eb5","tid":421201,"uid":107611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:49:41.000Z","msg":"正，遲下香港發揚呢個運動，強身健體"},{"pid":"677ddd2f1eaada6b8c13d687fa6ae9c8677c3e99","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T21:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774d3fb803a5600da143dfffe323b3533c7093b1","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f704f41c4d81b035fbd91bc86aff3304a4be9be8","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5e86501d5d665d0d2215885da9a8edd5309852","tid":421201,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"玩呢個運動可以講<br />\n唔撞得返去踢波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51caa8aa4d1a63663fadf118ba52a9e800331b89","tid":421201,"uid":119024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"睇過一次現場嘅波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8de094814c97a65b912c43e5b70cb50fe319f9","tid":421201,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-